  "description": "I\u0026rsquo;ve been making some amount of headway with organizing my office over the past few days, and generally feeling like I\u0026rsquo;m coming back into some sort of \u0026ldquo;form\u0026rdquo; with regards to working on my computer and doing other work. It\u0026rsquo;s tricky, because in times of certain crisis, I find myself answering lots of questions, which distracts from anything I might normally be doing, but, there\u0026rsquo;s not much space to dive into the specifics of what I\u0026rsquo;ve been doing in the meantime.\n",
